result.name: TeaWood Taiwanese Cafe & Restaurant

reviews.text: Yes, it is a famous Taiwanese dessert and noodle restaurant. It serves very standardized dish and quality as like others around Hong Kong. The staffs were kind and trying their best. This time, I tried oyster soup rice. It was as good as I expected. It may be very good for your upset stomach. Only I wished about this restaurant was pricings. I don't feel HKD80 is fair for a simple dinner.

In love with the braised beef noodles here. The noodle has a delicious chewy texture and the soup is very flavourful. If you don’t like thick noodles you can swap it out for vermicelli noodles instead. Also recommended the jasmine milk tea.
Good food selection and amiable staff.
Good food but quite fat... the minced pork is tasty... the dessert is quite big. a lot of choices...

Been here for a few times. Food was generally good and good portion. Today is the best experience so far. Thanks to Kelvin. His service is impeccable. All requests were delivered correctly with effeciency and smiles. His efforts should be recognised.

result.name: 茶木 · 台式休閒餐廳

reviews.text: 座位很舒適，不會想一般香港餐廳緊迫。餐點價格在這位置的話算不上貴，味道可口。炸雞排很台味，肉燥偏鹹，不過也算好吃，給的肉燥很大方，不會吃完剩白飯。飲料點了檸檬愛玉但是給的是細吸管XD
終於喺東涌搵到間可以食得到舒服及好食嘅食店， 價錢可接受一百蚊有找 ，起碼茶木仍然有水準。

Yes, it is a famous Taiwanese dessert and noodle restaurant. It serves very standardized dish and quality as like others around Hong Kong. The staffs were kind and trying their best. This time, I tried oyster soup rice. It was as good as I expected. It may be very good for your upset stomach. Only I wished about this restaurant was pricings. I don't feel HKD80 is fair for a simple dinner.

自從實行低碳飲食以來，難得在找到一款食極唔厭的餐點，而在東涌更難找到合適餐廳。
雖然這款煙三文魚極為普通，但因為職員Anson和Archer（唔知有冇串錯佢個名）的服務太貼心和親切，這是我從未在茶木感受過那種“食得很滋味”的愉快。
回到食物：這個沙律的菜一直以來都非常翠綠新鮮，煙三文魚有3大塊，份量適中，麻醬分開上，不會影響沙律質素。這裡的玫瑰咖啡已經含甜味，所以不用加糖，配咖啡的2小塊果仁脆餅，就令我在行低碳中仍忍不住口，還是放了在肚皮內。
回到入座時：是Anson領我們的，已經感受那種被受歡迎的招待，已經有多久沒有了這種期望？在今天，東涌茶木發生了。
運動後，今天有點鼻水，都要求餐飲要熱飲。但喜出望外的，Archer端來2杯暖水😍 又有多久，已經不敢在茶木要求一杯普通的水？今天，還是暖的，是一種表達對顧客慰問的溫暖。
真心想多謝2位，在現今的時代，2位實在是非常難得的年青人，有你們，香港有希望。
只有好老闆難求嗎？好員工亦言，茶木老闆，要好好珍惜這類員工喔～

In love with the braised beef noodles here. The noodle has a delicious chewy texture and the soup is very flavourful. If you don’t like thick noodles you can swap it out for vermicelli noodles instead. Also recommended the jasmine milk tea.
